reviews.title: No different
reviews.comment: Same as viewing the mobile website...would like to see save username ability and an actual app and not a web bowser in the app.
reviews.author: A Google User

reviews.title: Awesome so far.
reviews.comment: A little disappointed that checking your balance is just the mobile browser, but still super excited to finally have an app.
reviews.author: A Google User

reviews.title: Decent app.
reviews.comment: This app is great! It\'s so much easier to check on my account balance and transactions using this app than it is to use the actual website. It also has a cool feature which helps you find banks and ATMs for when you travel out of town.   I\'m only giving it a 4 star rating because it would not go into landscape mode. It seems stuck in portrait mode.
reviews.author: A Google User

reviews.title: Waste of resources
reviews.comment: I could never get the app to work and uninstalled it!
reviews.author: Jeffery Johnson
